    <item>
      <title>About</title>
      <link>https://acountia.no/en/about/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://acountia.no/en/about/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;div id=&#34;why-choose-us&#34; class=&#34;anchor-point&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;section class=&#34;value-wrap&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;value-left&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;h2 class=&#34;value-title&#34;&gt;Why do clients choose us?&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;    &lt;p class=&#34;value-lead&#34;&gt;When clients compare us with other accounting firms, they often highlight:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;value-grid&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;value-card&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;img class=&#34;value-icon&#34; src=&#34;https://acountia.no/images/icons/handshake.svg&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;h3&gt;Personal approach&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;      &lt;p&gt;Close follow-up, clear communication, and solutions tailored to your needs.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;value-card&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;img class=&#34;value-icon&#34; src=&#34;https://acountia.no/images/icons/target.svg&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;h3&gt;Long-term partnership&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;      &lt;p&gt;Stable routines, predictability, and collaboration that works over time.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;value-card&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;img class=&#34;value-icon&#34; src=&#34;https://acountia.no/images/icons/shield.svg&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;h3&gt;Quality and accuracy&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;      &lt;p&gt;Strong professional delivery with checks that reduce risk and errors.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;value-card&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;img class=&#34;value-icon&#34; src=&#34;https://acountia.no/images/icons/chip.svg&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;h3&gt;Modern systems&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;      &lt;p&gt;Efficient workflows in modern platforms with solid structure and documentation.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;value-card&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;img class=&#34;value-icon&#34; src=&#34;https://acountia.no/images/icons/chart.svg&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;h3&gt;Advisory that adds value&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;      &lt;p&gt;We use the numbers actively to support better decisions — not just reporting.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Bookkeeping</title>
      <link>https://acountia.no/en/services/bookkeeping/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://acountia.no/en/services/bookkeeping/</guid>
      <description>&lt;section class=&#34;service-bento service-bento--soft&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;service-bento-head&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;service-bento-tag&#34;&gt;Bookkeeping&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &lt;h2&gt;A bookkeeping setup that stays structured from the first transaction&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;    &lt;p&gt;We build routines that give you daily overview, reliable reporting, and better control throughout the year.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;service-bento-grid&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;      &#xA;      &#xA;      &#xA;      &lt;article class=&#34;service-bento-card&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;span class=&#34;service-bento-key&#34;&gt;Control&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;        &lt;h3&gt;Ongoing bookkeeping with structure&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;        &lt;p&gt;Transactions are recorded continuously with clear routines, proper documentation, and a steady workflow.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/article&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;      &#xA;      &#xA;      &#xA;      &lt;article class=&#34;service-bento-card&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;span class=&#34;service-bento-key&#34;&gt;Accuracy&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;        &lt;h3&gt;Reconciliations that make the numbers reliable&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;        &lt;p&gt;We follow up balances, accounts, and deviations so the bookkeeping gives you a stronger basis for decisions.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/article&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;      &#xA;      &#xA;      &#xA;      &lt;article class=&#34;service-bento-card&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;span class=&#34;service-bento-key&#34;&gt;Overview&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;        &lt;h3&gt;Reporting you can actually use&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;        &lt;p&gt;You receive updated figures and clear summaries that make the business easier to manage.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Contact</title>
      <link>https://acountia.no/en/contact/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://acountia.no/en/contact/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Below you’ll find our contact form and contact details.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;section class=&#34;service-bento service-bento--soft&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;service-bento-head&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;service-bento-tag&#34;&gt;Contact&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &lt;h2&gt;How we follow up when you contact us&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;    &lt;p&gt;We want it to be easy to get started. That is why we reply with clear answers, the right point of contact and a structured next step.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;service-bento-grid&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;      &#xA;      &#xA;      &#xA;      &lt;article class=&#34;service-bento-card&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;span class=&#34;service-bento-key&#34;&gt;Dialogue&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;        &lt;h3&gt;We start with your needs&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;        &lt;p&gt;Tell us briefly what you need help with and we will quickly see whether it relates to accounting, payroll, pricing or switching accountant.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
