    <item>
      <title>Outsourcing</title>
      <link>https://acountia.no/en/services/outsourcing/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://acountia.no/en/services/outsourcing/</guid>
      <description>&lt;section class=&#34;service-bento service-bento--calm&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;service-bento-head&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;service-bento-tag&#34;&gt;Outsourcing&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &lt;h2&gt;When you want to move tasks out, but keep control&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;    &lt;p&gt;We support businesses that want relief from administrative and financial tasks without losing overview, clarity, or momentum.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;service-bento-grid&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;      &#xA;      &#xA;      &#xA;      &lt;article class=&#34;service-bento-card&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;span class=&#34;service-bento-key&#34;&gt;Relief&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;        &lt;h3&gt;More time for operations and growth&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;        &lt;p&gt;We take responsibility for selected tasks so you can focus more on customers, leadership, and development.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/article&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;      &#xA;      &#xA;      &#xA;      &lt;article class=&#34;service-bento-card&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;span class=&#34;service-bento-key&#34;&gt;Structure&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;        &lt;h3&gt;Routines that work in practice&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;        &lt;p&gt;We establish clear workflows, contact points, and documentation that make collaboration easier.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/article&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;      &#xA;      &#xA;      &#xA;      &lt;article class=&#34;service-bento-card&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;span class=&#34;service-bento-key&#34;&gt;Scalability&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;        &lt;h3&gt;A setup that can grow with the business&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;        &lt;p&gt;The solution can be adapted both for smaller companies and for businesses in rapid growth.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Payroll</title>
      <link>https://acountia.no/en/services/payroll/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://acountia.no/en/services/payroll/</guid>
      <description>&lt;section class=&#34;service-bento service-bento--line&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;service-bento-head&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;service-bento-tag&#34;&gt;Payroll&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &lt;h2&gt;A payroll process with fixed routines and less friction&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;    &lt;p&gt;We make sure payroll, reporting, and follow-up are handled correctly every month, so you avoid unnecessary uncertainty.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;service-bento-grid&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;      &#xA;      &#xA;      &#xA;      &lt;article class=&#34;service-bento-card&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;span class=&#34;service-bento-key&#34;&gt;Timing&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;        &lt;h3&gt;Payroll delivered on schedule&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;        &lt;p&gt;We follow a fixed payroll rhythm so employees receive the correct payment at the expected time.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/article&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;      &#xA;      &#xA;      &#xA;      &lt;article class=&#34;service-bento-card&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;span class=&#34;service-bento-key&#34;&gt;Reliability&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;        &lt;h3&gt;Reporting without avoidable errors&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;        &lt;p&gt;Payroll submissions, holiday pay, deductions, and adjustments are handled with control and clear documentation.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/article&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;      &#xA;      &#xA;      &#xA;      &lt;article class=&#34;service-bento-card&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;span class=&#34;service-bento-key&#34;&gt;Fit&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;        &lt;h3&gt;Routines matched to your business&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;        &lt;p&gt;We adapt the payroll process to your staffing, work patterns, and the systems you already use.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Pricing</title>
      <link>https://acountia.no/en/prices/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://acountia.no/en/prices/</guid>
      <description>&lt;section class=&#34;service-bento service-bento--soft&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;service-bento-head&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;service-bento-tag&#34;&gt;Pricing&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &lt;h2&gt;A pricing model that is easy to understand&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;    &lt;p&gt;We want pricing discussions to feel clear, transparent and aligned with how your business actually operates.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;service-bento-grid&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;      &#xA;      &#xA;      &#xA;      &lt;article class=&#34;service-bento-card&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;span class=&#34;service-bento-key&#34;&gt;Scope&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;        &lt;h3&gt;Tailored to your business&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;        &lt;p&gt;We look at how your company is set up, which systems you use and how much follow-up you want from us.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/article&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;      &#xA;      &#xA;      &#xA;      &lt;article class=&#34;service-bento-card&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;span class=&#34;service-bento-key&#34;&gt;Clarity&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;        &lt;h3&gt;Clear picture of what is included&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;        &lt;p&gt;You should understand what is part of the ongoing delivery, which tasks we handle and how the collaboration is structured.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Privacy Policy</title>
      <link>https://acountia.no/en/privacy/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://acountia.no/en/privacy/</guid>
      <description>&lt;section class=&#34;privacy-wrap&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;privacy-grid&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;privacy-card&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;h3&gt;🔐 Data controller&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;      &lt;p&gt;Accountia Accounting is responsible for processing personal data through our website and services.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;privacy-card&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;h3&gt;📄 Data we collect&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;      &lt;p&gt;Contact details, inquiries via the contact form, and required client information.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;privacy-card&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;h3&gt;⚙️ Purpose&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;      &lt;p&gt;To respond to inquiries, deliver accounting services, and comply with legal requirements.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;privacy-card&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;h3&gt;🤝 Systems &amp;amp; processors&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;      &lt;p&gt;We use systems such as Tripletex, PowerOffice, DNB Regnskap, UniMicro and Fiken, adapted to client needs.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;privacy-card&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;h3&gt;🗂 Storage&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;      &lt;p&gt;Data is stored only as long as necessary or required by law.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
